changelogs.log:
Standardized prompt and improved log generation features.

- Updated prompt format to a standardized style.
- Enhanced prompt accuracy for LLM (large language model) interactions.
- Implemented working log generation functionality in Logify.
- Introduced `logify init` command for initial setup.
- Completed LLM summary feature integration.

Logify Initialization Bug Fix

- Fixed a bug that prevented logify from initializing correctly.

Update logify LLM logic

- Improved logic for logify functionality to enhance performance.
- Optimized data processing to reduce latency in generating logs.
- Fixed bugs related to previous log generation inconsistencies.

Changelog Revert

- Reverted recent changes to the changelog that may affect version tracking.
- Restored previous entries or states within the changelog for accurate history.

Logger Updates

- Improved logging messages for clarity and better debugging.
- Implemented basic logging functionality to capture essential application events.

New Logify functionality implemented

- Added a new logging feature to track application events.
- Improved performance of existing logging functions. 
- Fixed a bug that caused log entries to be saved incorrectly.
